These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, chinese, brazilian, british, colombian, russian, spanish
1. the chinese is in the middle##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the british##1
4. the pakistani is on the right of the brazilian##1
5. the spanish is on the far left##1
6. the russian is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | spanish | british | colombian | chinese | brazilian | pakistani | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  pilot, bartender, lawyer, police-officer, electrician, freelancer, coach
1. the coach is on the far right##1
2. the pilot is on the far left##1
3. the pilot is on the left of the electrician##1
4. the electrician is on the left of the lawyer##1
5. the police-officer is on the right of the freelancer##1
6. the coach is on the right of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | pilot | electrician | lawyer | freelancer | police-officer | bartender | coach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: gardening, photography, baking, skydiving, dancing, reading, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | dancing | gardening | reading | baking | traveling | photography | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-4::.
