.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different pets are kept: rat, frog, fish, horse, hamster, rabbit, dog
1. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | dog | fish | horse | rabbit | rat | frog | hamster |

