.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: musical, documentary, western, spy, animation, romance, scientific
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | documentary | musical | romance | spy | scientific | western |

